# Glassmorphic Login Form

A modern and responsive login form built using only HTML and CSS — with a beautiful glassmorphism effect.

## Features

- **Glassmorphic UI** with backdrop blur
- **Responsive Design** using Flexbox
- **Pure HTML & CSS** — no external libraries
- Neatly structured form with header, input fields, and submit button

## Live Demo

Click here to view live : https://khusi-gouda.github.io/Glassmorphic-form/
